title: Machine Gun Fellatio - Discography
description:
Australian rock band, complete studio recordings. 

Good arty groove with somewhat odd lyrics. Very addictive, especially Paging Mr. Strike.

Read all about them at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine_Gun_Fellatio
